'TEMPLATES'

Templates are a powerful tool for the GM to theme monsters and up the power level to increase the challenge for the players. 

Here are some example templates:

Spellstitched: Spellstitched creatures are undead that have been powerfully enhanced and fortified by arcane means. They are more dif- ficult to attack in melee and more resistant to being turned, and they gain the ability to cast spells. The process is much more effective when applied to intelligent undead than those that are mindless, since intelligent undead can discharge their spells tactically. CR+1, Complete Arcane P.161

Example: Skeletons w/ Cause Fear, Ghouls w/ Invisibility, 

